Help Type: command
Command: wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> get

Purpose:
  Inspect one queue job.

Usage:
  wikigraph wkg-job://<job-id> get [--json]

Arguments:
  <job-id>              Full job id or an unambiguous prefix.

Options:
  --json                Print a stable machine-readable job object.

Human output:
  Shows job id, state, archive path, chapter id, target, current step, workspace path, and error JSON when present.

Examples:
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e get
  wikigraph wkg-job://75d12f7e get --json
